metadata.name: GALAXIUX MEGAMI
metadata.description:
MY FIRST PIECE ON FND ! ! !

START the journey with MEGAMI in my style ! Fan art of Naoki Saito's super kawaii amazing project ! !    

I draw what i love in this megami - pink color , white hair, pajamas, also a little heart !!  

I try to draw a little cute glitter that I love to draw when I'm child in the background. Hope it make my megami cuter ! Also hope u'all like my megami !
